[thinking] I’m considering whether to declare a class as public static final. If the constructor is public, then the type of the nested public static inside a public test class would also be public. It seems like getConstructor should only retrieve public constructors of a public class. Also, if my inner class is public, and its enclosing class is also public, that makes sense. I noticed that Object.clone is protected and not accessible for public use. Good to keep in mind!
