[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating access modifiers**\n\nI’m considering whether to declare a class as public static final. If the constructor is public, then the type of the nested public static inside a public test class would also be public. It seems like getConstructor should only retrieve public constructors of a public class. Also, if my inner class is public, and its enclosing class is also public, that makes sense. I noticed that Object.clone is protected and not accessible for public use. Good to keep in mind!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_03b7c9dffe636479016a23ae163b388195b28b1c8313cf4132\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqI64q8Hgg1wpK1liCPx9lXJ-nFEXBZpUaM-LkoAYnA36DaxxNISY_P5DU6mwpaCzZhmr8hRHdp8HfX-s1ZqX31l2av4DudrJURmG2Q4lYWRPy4iosNeqnoBqtSp3bpuLHDD8T37_DiQml4ujSGv3dzyXIL4iTSNfM29aeQcsuvvv-GFVV2P_Sijnj9H4JPZd_3H-OfW4TxF32deKM2KE_BCy9gsZI3xfrvlkf5ApqhazTId0lJGo2sN9dsWFMlQjCFmb5VMF2nJbDUIfXoxPbbNnUPjG3E1NJj8cfmLboUjBoyGPos5P7MdEo4BO0qsiw4uFdzn4M2A0Ai6t5HhknIcADMlLvThBIEGLdynvvL-h__Djzm3LoZqyT8G-G8T6Cjq-S-Njw3pQ5iwA6AIiVYVG_v4XHUt3lba5nLjR8DL76n4q6ZcWmLTL4uaIowJGH5gu-Fguh-MhPJ5h9Zfv9h90khpDwIpyEDN7lGa23O8f4TvDWJ4-xECSDKMrV2mWFyVZ8UJaRZc7ehHbUX7r7crAfbgghitxBWSEj1M12VdWGTf05qn1zRsQ0mRAFlAqJNwHMbhRzMdyIdrjn3lbya5tpNti7BYgMU7ObNpDadG4zBfy_E-fdYsv5f0gyfSsBXgb8UGs8rjgjEmG1qGoEHDE-EcEaXV6j15oMT9YizNiPYVXMJ-tpPJkF8ybGyZCjbE1XnNCFWWndPxyA_0fZunWeIt7JxLYSA_v7A-p7RCdtFcbVsG8aZn_6a_SWSeXjVPt2wO2xvQBzlFrKQZoEKJBzrn-0hd-goSf_7a3qrt5hrlvHW5_7_QwaNHlw6oHqSxlyjou4lL5rd0VuVOOecHpaYjzQ1S91XPSR45XBRuhKvRW0j09pl44cwsOBGEJoUDZvSge4zslK06B7orm3vkcL_0ZWTB4WOVwIdv374CzZy8lq_oaP9EBouuwHDPl5defldH8_NdJK5qhlaw2zbsGQ5g_7Z31rPMHI6pbTcUl4hhQrrzOZE9Ng9-OtCOIf6qdqlshupa4mWcanGrInNTyt05KToVil8C9yY6rLN7AE7cy5k4h4uGHEAvq47U4CDKgR8Y-VZVlPz4GtvjEvyoqAb7ozh0ZznwCS65tS4dSUQFDoMuKAtwyLMwazhaPWKFJQchT0vlLUwG6QmbNJcBfiYUZvwo3KgJH78O-BvmqQT3GEymGvxlHJeRJgjxRkvKpwYwQlQ_eFS7